      "title": "An unidentified dead body washed up on Galumuvadora beach",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A dead body washed up on the Gallumudoora beach in Colombo today (29) afternoon.",
        "The police suspect that he is a person aged 30-40 years.",
        "This person is topless and is wearing black long pants.",
        "Due to being in the water for several days, it is seen that the skin has come off in places on the body."
      ],
